<p><font color="#000000" size="4"><strong>NMCARETPOSITION</strong></font></p>

<table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="3" width="100%">
    <tr>
        <td width="100%" bgcolor="#E6E6E6"><pre>typedef struct tagNMCARETPOSITION
{
	NMHDR	hdr;
	POINT	ptCaretPos;
} NMCARETPOSITION, FAR *LPNMCARETPOSITION;
</pre>
        </td>
    </tr>
</table>

<p>Contains information about a <a href="nmcaretpos.htm">NMBC_CARETPOSITION</a> notification message.</p>

<dl>
    <dt><em>hdr</em></dt>
    <dd><strong>NMHDR</strong> structure containing information about this notification message.</dd>
    <dt><em>ptCaretPos</em></dd>
    <dd><strong>POINT</strong> structure containing the current line/column position of the caret.</dd>
</dl>

